column1: NGR is adjacent to the dam of Rudyard Reservoir and, which is the only location that matches the stated altitude in the vicinity of the dam.
The 1850s record is annual totals only and may not be the same location as the other years.
There is a note that the gauge was moved in 1892 but with no details.
Negative comments made by the inspector for years 1882, 1887, 1898, 1900, 1901 and 1903
